records.name: Ja Manafaru, Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Manafaru Island, JA Manafaru, Maldives is in a rural area and on a private beach. While the natural beauty of Medhafushi and Govvaafushi can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Baarah Dock. Utheemu Palace and Maldives Climate Observatory are two other places to visit that come recommended. Water tubing, fishing, and swimming offer great chances to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with hiking/biking trails nearby.
